Date: Wed, 19 Nov 2025 19:05:09 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 44/74] FEDORA: 1590014 - hplip PPD search doesn't expect '-'
 in device name

Also:

  - 1912147 - Enable matching for '<model>_series' drivers in PPD search algorithm
  - remove the old search algorithm

Signed-off-by: Zdenek Dohnal <zdohnal@redhat.com>

Link: https://src.fedoraproject.org/rpms/hplip/blob/bfad24d925d28df17c78a991998071c702ba15e3/f/hplip-find-driver.patch
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
